<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good Morning Raffae=
lla</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you for your e=
mails and apologies for the delay in responding to you.</span><o:p></o:p></p=
>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Firstly, to acknowl=
edge the Privacy request has been received and passed onto our Privacy Team.=
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Also acknowledging t=
hat you wish all correspondence to be via email.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal">I am aware that you have met on site at your propert=
y yesterday with Grant Metson and that as proposed Tower will send you the d=
ocumented process.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">In addition to this=
 I have reviewed the information with regards to the expenses and can confir=
m the following will be paid under your Temporary Accommodation Benefit (lim=
it of $30,000.00 which is the higher
 of the two policy benefits) </span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">$1,452.00&nbsp;&nbs=
p;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6 nights Esplanade H=
otel
</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">$5,000.00 &nbsp;&nb=
sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rent @ $1,000.00 per week</spa=
n><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">$727.38 &nbsp;&nbsp=
;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Moving c=
osts to temp accommodation
</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">$7,179.38&nbsp;&=
nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Total of Temporary Acc=
ommodation benefit used to date.</span></b><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The other two payme=
nts as follows will be under your Contents claim as part of your sum insured=
.
</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">$340&nbsp;&nbsp;&nb=
sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&=
nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; cleaning of clothes
</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">$454.25&nbsp; &nbsp=
;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; cleaning=
 of sofa
</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">With regards to your=
 query if Stress Benefit applies, unfortunately it only applies if the prope=
rty and/or Contents is a Total Loss as per following policy wording,
</span><span style=3D"color:black">if the contents are deemed a total loss t=
hen we will proactively let you know of any changes to your eligibility for t=
his benefit.&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">House </span></b=
><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Stress benefit l=
ump sum payment</span></i><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We=E2=80=99ll pa=
y you a lump sum for the stress caused to you if your entire house is destro=
yed.</span></i><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We pay this bene=
fit in addition to your sum insured.</span></i><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Limit</span></i>=
<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We=E2=80=99ll pa=
y a maximum of $1,000 for each event as soon as we=E2=80=99ve accepted your h=
ouse claim</span></i><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Contents </span>=
</b><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Stress benefit l=
ump sum payment</span></i><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We=E2=80=99ll pa=
y you a lump sum for the stress caused to you if all your contents are destr=
oyed.</span></i><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">This benefit is i=
n addition to your contents sum insured.</span></i><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Limit</span></i>=
<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We=E2=80=99ll pa=
y a maximum of $2,000 for each event as soon as we have accepted your conten=
ts
</span></i><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">claim.</span></i=
><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please advise if=
 you are happy for these payments to be made to your nominated account on fi=
le where the premiums are deducted from or wish to supply an alternative acc=
ount.<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Just reach out if y=
ou have any further questions as always, I am happy to assist.</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Kind Regards</span>=
<o:p></o:p></p>
